{"article_id":"eOnqL60iWWZinmkC","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"SANTA ROSA , Calif. --","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"An onslaught of relentless wildfires across a wide swath of Northern California broke out almost simultaneously","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"and then grew exponentially ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"swallowing up properties from wineries to trailer parks","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and tearing through both tiny rural towns and urban subdivisions .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"At least 13 people are dead ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"at least 100 injured","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"and at least 1,500 homes and businesses destroyed ,","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"authorities said .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"All three figures are expected to surge in coming days","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"as more information is reported .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Many homes and businesses were evacuated","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"-- some just in the nick of time","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"as flames approached .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Vice President Mike Pence ,","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"who is visiting California ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"announced","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that President Trump approved a `` major disaster declaration '' for the state","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to assist in the response .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"Pence ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"who received a briefing on the wildfires ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"17 were burning in Northern California .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"`` It 's heartbreaking to think","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"that many of the fallen represent our most vulnerable , in some cases senior citizens","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"who simply were not able to escape the flames","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"that overcame their homes , ''","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"Pence said .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"`` They 're in our prayers . ''","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"Taken as a group ,","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"the wildfires are already among the deadliest in California history .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"CBS San Francisco reports","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"the fires have consumed nearly 107,000 acres","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and turned whole neighborhoods into piles of ashes .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"Residents","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"who gathered at emergency shelters and grocery stores","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"they were shocked by the speed and ferocity of the flames .","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"They recalled all the possessions","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"they had left behind .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"`` All that good stuff , I 'm never going to see it again , ''","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"said Jeff Okrepkie ,","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"who fled his neighborhood in Santa Rosa","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"knowing","depth":15},{"id":44,"text":"it was probably the last time","depth":16},{"id":45,"text":"he would see his home of the past five years standing .","depth":16},{"id":46,"text":"His worst fears were confirmed Monday ,","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"when a friend sent him a photo of what was left :","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"a smoldering heap of burnt metal and debris .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"Some of the largest of the blazes","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"burning over a 200-mile region","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"were in Napa and Sonoma counties ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"home to dozens of wineries","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"that attract tourists from around the world .","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"They sent smoke as far south as San Francisco , about 60 miles away .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Sonoma County said","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"it has received more than 100 missing-person reports","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"as family and friends scramble to locate loved ones .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"The reports have come via calls to a hotline","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"the county set up for the missing ,","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"according to Scott Alonso , communications director for Sonoma County .","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"It 's possible that many or most of the missing are safe","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"but simply ca n't be reached","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"because of the widespread loss of cell service and other communications .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"As of Monday evening , 99,000 Pacific Gas & Electric customers were without power","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"because of the wildfires in Northern California , a majority in Napa and Sonoma counties ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"PG & E officials told CBS San Francisco .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"In addition , PG & E crews had shut off gas service to about 26,000 customers as a precaution","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"because flames can damage a gas pipe or meter ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"the station said .","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Workers in the renowned Northern California wine country picked through charred debris","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"and struggled with what to do","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"after wildfires swept through lush vineyards ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"destroying at least two wineries","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"and damaging many others .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"The wind-driven wildfires came","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"as Napa and Sonoma counties were finishing highly anticipated harvests of wine grapes .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"Monday normally would have found workers picking and processing the ripe grapes","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"to make chardonnay and other wines .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Instead , melted and blackened wine bottles decorated the ruined Signorello Estate winery in Napa Valley .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"People at Paradise Ridge Winery in Sonoma County posted photos of debris and haze ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"they were `` heartbroken to share the news ''","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"that the winery had burned .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Much of the damage in Northern California was in Santa Rosa , a far larger and more developed city","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"than usually finds itself at the mercy of a wildfire .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"The city is home to 175,000 residents ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"including both the wine-country wealthy and the working class .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"The flames were unforgiving to both groups .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Hundreds of homes of all sizes were leveled by flames so hot","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"they melted the glass off cars","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"and turned aluminum wheels into liquid .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"Former San Francisco Giants pitcher Noah Lowry ,","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"who now runs an outdoor sporting goods store in Santa Rosa ,","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"was forced to flee in minutes along with his wife , two daughters and a son just over 2 weeks old .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"`` I ca n't shake hearing people scream in terror","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"as the flames barreled down on us , ''","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"Lowry said .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"His family and another","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"evacuating with them","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"tried to take U.S. 101","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"but found it blocked by flames ,","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"and had to take country roads","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"to get to the family friends","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"who took them in .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"To the south , in Orange County , more than 5,000 homes were evacuated","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"because of a rapidly spreading brush fire in the Anaheim area .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"The blaze had grown to nearly 10 square miles","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and had destroyed dozens of structures .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"The blaze has scorched 6,000 acres","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"and destroyed dozens of structures in Orange County .","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Plumes of smoke were visible over Disneyland ,","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"and officials issued air quality warnings for parts of Los Angeles County .","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"An Anaheim police spokesman says","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"there 's been no containment so far .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"Among those","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"fleeing the flames in Northern California","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"were what the San Francisco Chronicle calls `` a who 's who of athletes","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"-- Olympians , Hall of Famers . ''","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"The newspaper says","depth":8},{"id":120,"text":"they 'd gathered","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"to attend retired football star Ronnie Lott 's celebrity fundraiser at Mayacama Golf Club in Santa Rosa .","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"`` Former Giants outfielder Barry Bonds wound up shuttling guests","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"who did not have rides away from Mayacama","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"when the villas at the course were evacuated , ''","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"the Chronicle reports .","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"`` Longtime Kansas City pitcher Bret Saberhagen left his golf clubs in the parking lot","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"in order to fit Olympic speedskater Dan Jansen and his wife into his rental car .","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"And onetime Dodgers closer Eric Gagne raised the alarm at a second hotel","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"to which the celebrities were sent ,","depth":10},{"id":130,"text":"pounding on doors","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"to make sure","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"occupants were out . ''","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"A 90-mile stretch of the highway is framed by the flames","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"and has been a major concern overnight ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"said Brad Alexander , a spokesman for the California Office of Emergency Services .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"Highway 12 ,","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"which winds through the heart of wine country ,","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"was also rendered unusable by the flames .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"`` Sonoma and Napa counties have been hit very hard , ''","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"Alexander said .","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"The ferocity of the flames forced authorities to focus primarily on getting people out safely ,","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"even if it meant abandoning structures to the fire .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"Firefighters rushed to a state home for the severely disabled","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"when flames reached one side of the center 's sprawling campus in the historic Sonoma County town of Glen Ellen .","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"Crews got the more than 200 people from the threatened buildings ,","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"one firefighter said ,","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"as flames closed within a few dozen feet .","depth":12},{"id":148,"text":"Fires from ruptured gas lines dotted the smoky landscapes of blackened Santa Rosa hillsides .","depth":12},{"id":149,"text":"Fire trucks raced by smoldering roadside landscaping in search of higher priorities .","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"The flames were fickle in some corners of the city .","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"One hillside home remained unscathed","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"while a dozen surrounding it","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"were destroyed .","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"Kim Hoe , a 33-year-old tech worker from Penang , Malaysia , was staying at the Hilton Sonoma Wine Country ,","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"which was gutted by flames .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"the power went out around 1 a.m. ,","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"and he and his colleagues started packing up","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"when someone knocked on the door","depth":14},{"id":160,"text":"and told them to run .","depth":14},{"id":161,"text":"`` We just had to run","depth":14},{"id":162,"text":"and run .","depth":14},{"id":163,"text":"It was full of smoke .","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"We could barely breathe , ''","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"Hoe said .","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"The large majority of the injured were treated for smoke inhalation ,","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"according to St. Joseph Health ,","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"which operates hospitals in the Santa Rosa area .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"Two were in critical condition","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"and one was in serious condition .","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"The number of injured is expected to climb","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"as information comes in for all the other areas","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"affected by the firestorm","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"consuming the state .","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"October has generally been the most destructive time of year for California wildfires .","depth":6},{"id":176,"text":"What was unusual Sunday , however , was to have so many fires take off at the same time .","depth":6},{"id":177,"text":"Other than the windy conditions","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"that helped drive them all ,","depth":7},{"id":179,"text":"there was no known connection between the fires ,","depth":7},{"id":180,"text":"and no cause has been released for any of them .","depth":7},{"id":181,"text":"But the conditions late Monday and early Tuesday were calmer","depth":6},{"id":182,"text":"than they were 24 hours earlier ,","depth":6},{"id":183,"text":"bringing hopes of progress against the flames .","depth":5},{"id":184,"text":"Gov . Jerry Brown declared a state of emergency for the fire areas ,","depth":5},{"id":185,"text":"and asked the federal government to do the same .","depth":5},{"id":186,"text":"Pence said at an event near Sacramento","depth":6},{"id":187,"text":"that the federal government stands with California","depth":7},{"id":188,"text":"as it takes on the blazes ,","depth":7},{"id":189,"text":"but he made no specific promises .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":379,"left":0,"right":378,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":378,"left":363,"right":377,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":363,"left":252,"right":362,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":252,"left":217,"right":251,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":217,"left":202,"right":216,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":193,"right":201,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":193,"left":191,"right":192,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":191,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":192,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":198,"right":200,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":198,"left":196,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":195,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":5,"right":194,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":194,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":197,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":11,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":216,"left":206,"right":215,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":204,"right":205,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":204,"left":203,"right":16,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":209,"